        {
            "title": "滬深A股早市倒跌成交增 深指失守萬五關 紫金等有色金屬股受壓",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市今早反覆下滑，滬深兩市股指均中止之前的連升成績，深指更失守萬五關；紫金礦業(02899)等有色金屬股明顯捱沽。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指今早輕微高開4點，初段已見半日高位，最高報4114點，升8點，開市不足15分鐘已轉跌，早市尾段反覆試底，最低曾見4072點，跌33點；滬指中午收報4073點，跌32點或0.79%，半日成交增至8593.35億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指同樣高開低走，初段出現的半日高位15248點時僅升71點，未幾便開始倒跌且反覆向下走勢，早市尾段失守萬五關，最低見14940點，跌237點；深指中午收報14945點，跌232點或1.53%，成交達1.09萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數也跌38點或0.79%，收報4761點；創業板指數更挫68點或1.83%，報3684點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241107_FI_source-ap_China_Financial_Markets-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">有色金屬板塊資金流出較明顯，紫金礦業A股(601899.SH)跌3.77%，報34.19元；赤峰黃金(06693)A股(600988.SH)更跌5.69%，報40.76元。稀土類股跌勢更勁，中稀有色(600259.SH)跌停板，中國稀土(000831.SZ)跌7.38%，北方稀土(600111.SH)跌5.76%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">石油等資源股逆市造好，中國海油(00883)A股(600938.SH)升3.21%，報38.28元；中煤能源(01898)A股(601898.SH)漲5.48%，報17.7元；兗礦能源(01171)A股(600188.SH)升4.13%，報20.7元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909868-%e6%bb%ac%e6%b7%b1a%e8%82%a1%e6%97%a9%e5%b8%82%e5%80%92%e8%b7%8c%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e5%a2%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e5%a4%b1%e5%ae%88%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%94%e9%97%9c-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e7%ad%89%e6%9c%89",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-23 11:44:39",
