        {
            "title": "恒瑞醫藥首季盈利升逾1% 今早初段股價逆市造好",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒瑞醫藥(01276)昨天收市後派首季成績表，盈利增長逾20%；該股今早逆市造好，最多超超過6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早一度衝上71.3元，升6.66%；截至上午約10時16分報69.9元，升幅收窄至4.56%，暫時成交已達2.61億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15909417-%e6%81%92%e7%91%9e%e9%86%ab%e8%97%a5%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1-%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e9%80%a0%e5%a5%bd",
